title: Dragon Ball Z Kai - Season 1 - English
description:
Dragon Ball Z Kai the complete first season with English audio only.
Season 1 is from the beginning up the the end of the Cell Saga.

I took two torrents already available, the complete Japanese uncut season 1 and the season 1 audio pack with English funimation voices.
Then manually muxed them together removing the Japanese audio and moving the English audio up with 3900ms as described in the audio pack torrent.
It was alot of manual labour so I hope you enjoy it!

This is also my first torrent so bear with me because it is a large torrent and my seeding speed is limited (max 9 Mbit).
